text: Mississippi Highway 782 (MS 782) is a state highway located in the U.S. State of Mississippi. Located entirely within Mantee in Webster County, the western terminus of the route is at the western terminus of MS 46, where it continues as Main Street and the eastern terminus is at MS 15. Unlike most of the Mississippi Highways numbered between 701 and 992, MS 782 is signed. ==Route description== MS 782 starts at a three-way intersection with MS 46 on the west side of Mantee. Continuing as Main Street from MS 46, the road intersects Skelton Street. The street then intersects three driveways and ends at an intersection with MS 15. ==Major intersections== ==References== 782 Category:Transportation in Webster County, Mississippi Category:State highways in the United States shorter than one mile
